{"tid":898004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Model不再瘦！日本百貨大膽啟用「禿頭、肉肉人模」","createTime":"2018-11-11T11:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T13:43:26.000Z","uid":122,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9eef30f503ed45f55a545b1ce255a58c50e6e1de","tid":898004,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"愛逛街的你常常被櫥窗中的模特吸引，它們穿著最新款的時裝，渾身上下散發出迷人的氣質。心血來潮的你毫不猶豫的買下整套服裝，直到看到鏡子中的自己才恍然大悟。日本Sogo百貨在官方推特秀出了最新版的「人形模特」，並引發了一系列大膽創新的「非常規人形模特」。<br />\n<br />\n▼日本Sogo百貨的橫濱店和大宮店將這些造型獨特的模特發布在推特上，招募可以擺出同款造型的店員。於是不少網友看到後紛紛前來應徵，最終Sogo百貨因為造型獨特的模特賺得盆缽滿滿，收益遠遠超過傳統廣告。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.omgtw.com/upload/article/original/5dca38ca500b625a414d19f9c610f8c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.omgtw.com%2Fupload%2Farticle%2Foriginal%2F5dca38ca500b625a414d19f9c610f8c7.jpg&h=d71ba59b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.omgtw.com/upload/article/original/32684112cc12088a36afc838318911d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.omgtw.com%2Fupload%2Farticle%2Foriginal%2F32684112cc12088a36afc838318911d9.jpg&h=a91812b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n▼看到商機的商家也紛紛採用了「非常規人形模特」，各種「不完美」模特紛紛上市。日本推特網友@M_T在逛街時發現的「發福模特」並發文：「這真的太貼心太實用了！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.omgtw.com/upload/article/original/8ddcef0ea4a8df5f2a48cde15b4d070a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.omgtw.com%2Fupload%2Farticle%2Foriginal%2F8ddcef0ea4a8df5f2a48cde15b4d070a.jpg&h=0e31ebb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼還有讓女性消費者極度舒適的「小肚腩模特」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.omgtw.com/upload/article/original/74bf3d3adc9fbb0f16edeedcd4bad199.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.omgtw.com%2Fupload%2Farticle%2Foriginal%2F74bf3d3adc9fbb0f16edeedcd4bad199.jpg&h=ece7ee26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.omgtw.com/upload/article/original/827e5eb0a1b3f530e90dc91f4a2d130b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.omgtw.com%2Fupload%2Farticle%2Foriginal%2F827e5eb0a1b3f530e90dc91f4a2d130b.jpg&h=22d7e9cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.omgtw.com/upload/article/original/6daa258d08b6f851253c091dda1d80b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.omgtw.com%2Fupload%2Farticle%2Foriginal%2F6daa258d08b6f851253c091dda1d80b2.jpg&h=8cce0f5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.omgtw.com/upload/article/original/fb389ea0cd14e6e2f566f53db221e6e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.omgtw.com%2Fupload%2Farticle%2Foriginal%2Ffb389ea0cd14e6e2f566f53db221e6e4.jpg&h=e8263752&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9bfd94313dc74adc8f6d09ad953e93627f59628","tid":898004,"uid":51701,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:25:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkcd.com/userfiles/1498176594.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fuserfiles%2F1498176594.jpg&h=ce427d54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/756322/org/28cdbac7416c58957b143108caf8bfb3.jpg/iOCe3eifRICLvF46g3rcwsTXfmWBBbZDjwl3Q48Jd0M?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F756322%2Forg%2F28cdbac7416c58957b143108caf8bfb3.jpg%2FiOCe3eifRICLvF46g3rcwsTXfmWBBbZDjwl3Q48Jd0M%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=70a4b8ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/2pjht6eyJ8Q/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F2pjht6eyJ8Q%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=e2a8212b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130519/photo/0519-00176-021b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientalda